<item>
            <title>[LU-20151] Sanity-sec 26 slow due to dynamic nodemap removal check</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-20151</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It appears that &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19478&quot; title=&quot;dynamic nodemaps are not removed when persistent nodemaps are changed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-19478&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-19478&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; nodemap: clear dyn nodemaps when config is changed | &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/62808&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/62808&lt;/a&gt; may have caused a slowdown in sanity-sec test_26 (create and destroy 32000 nodemaps) when it landed on 2026-01-07, going from ~400s per run to ~2000s per run, according to the subtest duration page:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/reports?test_set_script_id=5984404e-4b34-11e0-a7f6-52540025f9af&amp;amp;sub_test_script_id=de315ec4-4523-11e5-a64b-5254006e85c2&amp;amp;source=duration_trend#redirect&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/reports?test_set_script_id=5984404e-4b34-11e0-a7f6-52540025f9af&amp;amp;sub_test_script_id=de315ec4-4523-11e5-a64b-5254006e85c2&amp;amp;source=duration_trend#redirect&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(see attachment)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
